CONTACT
Good friends, close access to good churches and shopping, medical access…some of the few things this community and town have to offer.
Julie
Resident
There’s plenty of activities and great people here. And the park stays remarkably clean.
Wayne & Sharon
Resident
It’s easy and convenient to get around the town in a vehicle, but when we’re not venturing out we love it right here inside the community.
Russell & Glenda
Resident
I like the location of the park. I like the people. I like the price.
Daphne
Resident
Our son lives in Lakeland, so it’s great to have found a place we enjoy being at and offers the benefit of still being close to our family.
Alma & David
Resident
I’m a renter, and I love the weather and the ‘no snow’ effect while I’m here! Any issue I’ve had has always been handled quickly, and I even stay in touch with some of the residents when I’m at my second home up north.
Herm
Resident
We found this place online, bought our place sight unseen, and we love it here at Lakeland Estates.
Don & Lori
Resident
I was a Vietnam pilot, I’ve worked for businesses all over the country, and now I’m an adjunct aeronautic professor at a local college. Lakeland Estates is my home and affords me the ability to remain active and mobile.
Frank
Resident
